#

Garlic Butter Steak Bites with Mashed Potatoes and Green Beans

$20
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

EasyQuickSavory

Description

Tender steak bites sautéed in a rich garlic butter sauce, served with creamy mashed potatoes and fresh green beans for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Steak (Sirloin or Tenderloin): 1 pound
  • Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper (freshly ground): to taste
  • Potatoes (Yukon Gold or Russet): 2 pounds
  • Milk: 1/2 cup
  • Green Beans (trimmed): 1 pound
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
